---

<MainLayout
  title="SRP Portfolio | Personal Professional Profile"
  description="Sara Ringkow Petersen's digital resume, showcasing her skills, experience, and selected cases from her studies."
  ogtitle="Personal Professional Profile – SRP Portfolio"
  ogdescription="Take a look at Sara Ringkow Petersen's personal professional profile – a digital resume, showcasing skills, experience, and selected cases from her studies."
  ogimage="/other/hero_image.webp"
>
  <!-- SECTION: Hero -->
  <div
    class="hero-section top-content text-pale-50 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 pb-20 pt-40 md:pb-28 grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"
  >
    <div>
      <h1
        id="h1"
        class="hero-title-entrance title text-display-mobile xl:text-display-desktop text-center xl:text-left md:pb-12 pb-6 uppercase text-pale-50"
      >
        Sara Ringkow Petersen
      </h1>
      <h2
        id="h2"
        class="hero-title-entrance subtitle text-h2-mobile xl:text-h2-desktop italic font-light text-center xl:text-left tracking-wide text-pale-50"
      >
        Multimedia Designer & Concept Developer
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image-entrance">
      <div class="hero-image-wrap">
        <img src="/other/hero_image.webp" alt="Sara Ringkow Petersen" class="hero-image" loading="eager" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION: About -->
  <div class="main-content1 max-w-7xl mx-6 md:mx-8 xl:max-w-6xl xl:mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pb-30 md:pb-60">
    <div id="info" class="left-content text-pale-50">
      <h3 class="section-heading text-h3-mobile md:text-h3-desktop pb-4">Who am I?</h3>
      <p class="text-p-mobile md:text-p-desktop">
        My name is Sara Ringkow Petersen, a Multimedia Designer and Concept Developer based in <span class="accent-text font-bold">Copenhagen</span>.
        I design and build accessible websites, interfaces, and concepts&mdash; focusing on structure, clarity, and the people who use them. I'm
        currently interning at <span class="accent-text font-bold">Folkæt</span>, alongside studying a top-up Bachelor's in Digital Concept
        Development.
      </p>
      <p class="text-p-mobile md:text-p-desktop mt-5">
        I'm dedicated to creating <span class="accent-text font-bold">accessible, user-friendly digital solutions</span> by blending my technical skills
        in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like Astro and Tailwind with a creative approach. I'm experienced in design tools like Figma and project
        management methods such as SCRUM and Trello.
      </p>
      <p class="text-p-mobile md:text-p-desktop mt-5">
        As someone late-diagnosed with <span class="accent-text font-bold">autism and ADD</span>, I know what it's like to use digital platforms that
        weren't built with you in mind&mdash; that perspective drives my commitment to inclusive design, making digital platforms better for everyone,
        especially those with special needs.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div id="pfp" class="right-content flex justify-center pt-10 xl:pt-20 pb-32">
      <img
        src="/other/pfp2.webp"
        alt="Portrait of Sara Ringkow Petersen"
        class="portrait-image about-portrait w-[200px] h-[200px] xl:w-[350px] xl:h-[400px] object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION: Timeline -->
  <div id="timeline" class="timeline max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 flex justify-center md:justify-center md:max-w-6xl pb-20 md:pb-60">
    <div class="left-content text-pale-50">
      <h3 class="section-heading text-h3-mobile md:text-h3-desktop text-left pb-6">The highlights of my journey</h3>

      <div class="timeline-columns">
        <section class="timeline-column md:pb-0 pb-4" aria-labelledby="timeline-school">
          <h4 id="timeline-school" class="timeline-column-title">School</h4>
          <ol class="timeline-grid">
            {educationTimelineItems.map((item) => <TimelineItem {...item} />)}
          </ol>
        </section>

        <section class="timeline-column" aria-labelledby="timeline-work">
          <h4 id="timeline-work" class="timeline-column-title">Work</h4>
          <ol class="timeline-grid">
            {workTimelineItems.map((item) => <TimelineItem {...item} />)}
